'''ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯'''（'''ABL'''）是[[γ-丁内酯|γ-丁内酯]]的衍生物，可用于[[有机合成|有机合成]]，也用于鉴定[[伯胺|伯胺]]。<ref name="Sabry">{{Cite journal |last=Sabry |first=Suzy M. |date=2006 |title=Application of 2-acetylbutyrolactone to spectrofluorimetry: Fluorescence properties of Schiff bases derived from 2-acetylbutyrolactone and spectrofluorimetric determination of primary amine-containing compounds |url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0731708505006114 |journal=Journal of Pharmaceutical and Biomedical Analysis |language=en |volume=40 |issue=5 |pages=1057–1067 |doi=10.1016/j.jpba.2005.08.036|pmid=16256289 }}</ref>

== 制备==
ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯可以由[[乙酸酯|乙酸酯]]和[[γ-丁内酯|γ-丁内酯]]在[[碱|碱]]溶液中发生[[缩合反应|缩合反应]]而成。<ref name="Koehler">{{Cite web |last=Koehler |first=Guenther |date=August 4, 1998 |title=Method for Preparing 2-Acetyl-y-Butyrolactone |url=https://patents.google.com/patent/US5789603A/en |url-status=live |access-date=March 30, 2022 |website=United States Patent|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331171934/https://patents.google.com/patent/US5789603A/en |archive-date=2022-03-31 }}</ref>

== 用处==
=== 荧光检验===
ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯本身的荧光很微弱，但它的衍生物照到[[紫外线|紫外线]]时会发出很强的荧光。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":8">{{Cite journal |last=Sabry |first=S M |date=2006 |title=Enhanced Spectrophotometry of Sulfonamides with Novel 2‐Acetylbutyrolactone Derivatives |journal=Analytical Letters |volume=39 |issue=13 |pages=2591–2615 |doi=10.1080/00032710600824748 |s2cid=93950011}}</ref>ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯的[[羰基|羰基]]会和[[胺|胺]]反应生成[[希夫碱|希夫碱]]，因此经常用于在有机合成中确认合成出了胺。<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal |last=Sabry |first=S M |date=2006 |title=Application of 2-acetylbutyrolactone to spectrofluorimetry: Fluorescence properties of Schiff bases derived from 2-acetylbutyrolactone and spectrofluorimetric determination of primary amine-containing compounds |journal=Journal of Pharmaceutical and Biomedical Analysis |volume=40 |issue=5 |pages=1057–1067 |doi=10.1016/j.jpba.2005.08.036 |pmid=16256289}}</ref>ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯也可以和[[芳香胺|芳香胺]]发生[[雅普－克林格曼反应|雅普－克林格曼反应]]，生成荧光分子。<ref name=":8" />

=== 药物的前体 ===
ɑ-乙酰-γ-丁内酯是多种如{{link-de|檀香烯|Santalene}}<ref name=":5">{{Cite journal |last=Unnikrishnan |first=P,A |date=1992 |title=Syntheses of epi-β-Santalene, β-Santalene and an Isomer of β-Santalene with 4-Methyl-4-pentenyl Side Chain |journal= Synthetic Communications|volume=22 |issue=22 |pages=3159–3168 |doi=10.1080/00397919208021129}}</ref>的药物的前体。

